====Bill Nye–Ken Ham debate====
{{DYK nompage links|nompage=Bill Nye–Ken Ham debate|Bill Nye–Ken Ham debate}}
* ... that the February 4, 2014, '''[[Bill Nye–Ken Ham debate|debate between Bill Nye and Ken Ham]]''' on the viability of [[Young Earth creationism]] was watched by approximately 3 million people live on the Internet?
:* '''ALT1''':... that '''[[Bill Nye–Ken Ham debate|Ken Ham's debate with Bill Nye]]''' on the viability of [[Young Earth creationism]] spurred fundraising for the [[Ark Encounter]], a biblical theme park proposed by Ham's [[Answers in Genesis]] ministry?
